<div id="LC5" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">Creative Commons Corporation (&quot;Creative Commons&quot;) is not a law firm and</div>
<div id="LC6" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">does not provide legal services or legal advice. Distribution of</div>
<div id="LC7" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">Creative Commons public licenses does not create a lawyer-client or</div>
<div id="LC8" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">other relationship. Creative Commons makes its licenses and related</div>
<div id="LC9" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">information available on an &quot;as-is&quot; basis. Creative Commons gives no</div>
<div id="LC10" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">warranties regarding its licenses, any material licensed under their</div>
<div id="LC11" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">terms and conditions, or any related information. Creative Commons</div>
<div id="LC12" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">disclaims all liability for damages resulting from their use to the</div>
<div id="LC13" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">fullest extent possible.</div>
<div id="LC14" class="react-code-text react-code-line-contents-no-virtualization react-file-line html-div ">
